Steps
GCP
1. Create a service account
2. Give permissions
3. Create a JSON file and download the key
On-premise:
1. Install client libraries
pip install --upgrade google-cloud-storage
2. Set environment variable
$env:GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS="D:\Python-Learn\mercurial-smile-254413-21cad2137f64.json" (windows) #path
export GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS="/home/user/Downloads/[FILE_NAME].json" (Linux)
